<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.4">
<l>neñca mēnallai nallaiyuṉ ṉaippeṟṟā</l>
<l>leṉcey yōmiṉi yeṉṉa kuṟaiviṉa</l>
<l>mainta ṉaimala rāṇmaṇa vāḷaṉai</l>
<l>tuñcum pōtum viṭātu toṭarkkaṇṭāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart, you are good, you are good. If we have you</l>
<l>what can we not do? What do we lack now?</l>
<l>Without letting go even at the time of sleeping hold on</l>
<l>to the young man, the bridegroom of her on the flower, you who have seen [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
